## Game Overview
Nova Pouch is a single-player creativity web game. Players draw tokens from 3 colored pouches:
- Red: Object tokens (umbrella, shoes, clock, glasses, chair, cup, key, pillow)
- Blue: Attribute tokens (transparent, flying, singing, time-reversing, emotion-reading)  
- Green: Constraint tokens (mesh-like holes, dissolves in water, only works at night, single-use)

Players combine tokens and describe a world where such objects naturally exist.

